{
  "video_id": "deG_LTcAjaM",
  "title": "Did the global response to 9/11 make us safer? | Benedetta Berti",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13404.0,
      "end_time": 16680.0,
      "text": "Almost 20 years have passed since 9/11."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 18120.0,
      "end_time": 21336.0,
      "text": "It is time to take stock of where we stand"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21360.0,
      "end_time": 22800.0,
      "text": "and stop and think."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 24000.0,
      "end_time": 26960.0,
      "text": "It is time to ask ourselves,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26120.0,
      "end_time": 28256.0,
      "text": "have the assumptions and policies"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 28280.0,
      "end_time": 30576.0,
      "text": "we developed in the wake of those tragic events"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30600.0,
      "end_time": 33800.0,
      "text": "truly made us more secure?"
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 33880.0,
      "end_time": 38416.0,
      "text": "Have they made our societies, both in Europe and in the United States,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 38440.0,
      "end_time": 39640.0,
      "text": "more resilient?"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 40720.0,
      "end_time": 44735.0,
      "text": "I&#39;ve worked all my life in the field of security and defense,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 44759.0,
      "end_time": 47976.0,
      "text": "and I am convinced that now, more than ever,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 48000.0,
      "end_time": 53416.0,
      "text": "we need to radically reframe the way we think and act about security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 53440.0,
      "end_time": 55960.0,
      "text": "and especially about international security."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 57000.0,
      "end_time": 60616.0,
      "text": "By international security, I actually mean what we do,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 60640.0,
      "end_time": 61976.0,
      "text": "how we prepare our countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 62000.0,
      "end_time": 65495.0,
      "text": "to better respond and prevent external threats,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 65519.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67440.0,
      "text": "and how we protect our citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 68760.0,
      "end_time": 70456.0,
      "text": "The key to both"
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 70480.0,
      "end_time": 73136.0,
      "text": "is to focus on protecting civilians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 73160.0,
      "end_time": 74776.0,
      "text": "both in our own countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 74800.0,
      "end_time": 77720.0,
      "text": "and in those where we are present in the name of security."
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 79280.0,
      "end_time": 81936.0,
      "text": "Now, this idea goes against the fixed narrative"
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 81960.0,
      "end_time": 84696.0,
      "text": "that we developed over the past 20 years"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 84720.0,
      "end_time": 87400.0,
      "text": "over what security is and how to get it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 88400.0,
      "end_time": 93480.0,
      "text": "but that narrative is flawed, and worse, it is counterproductive."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 94680.0,
      "end_time": 96696.0,
      "text": "Over the past 20 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 96720.0,
      "end_time": 99496.0,
      "text": "both in the United States and in Europe,"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 99520.0,
      "end_time": 104336.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ve come to accept that we must talk about security in zero sum terms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 104360.0,
      "end_time": 109896.0,
      "text": "as if the only way to gain more security is by compromising on values and rights:"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 109920.0,
      "end_time": 113160.0,
      "text": "security versus human rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 113400.0,
      "end_time": 116976.0,
      "text": "safety versus freedom and development."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 117000.0,
      "end_time": 119496.0,
      "text": "This is a false opposition."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 119520.0,
      "end_time": 121216.0,
      "text": "It just doesn&#39;t work like that."
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 121240.0,
      "end_time": 123560.0,
      "text": "We need to recognize"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 123800.0,
      "end_time": 125896.0,
      "text": "that security and human rights are not opposite values,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 125920.0,
      "end_time": 128120.0,
      "text": "they are intrinsically related."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 129800.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132416.0,
      "text": "After all, the most basic human right"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 132440.0,
      "end_time": 135776.0,
      "text": "is the right to live and to be free from violence,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 135800.0,
      "end_time": 138816.0,
      "text": "and a state&#39;s most basic responsibility"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 138840.0,
      "end_time": 141199.0,
      "text": "is to guarantee that right for its citizens."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 141960.0,
      "end_time": 146136.0,
      "text": "Conversely, if we think about communities all over the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 146160.0,
      "end_time": 148856.0,
      "text": "affected by war and conflict,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 148880.0,
      "end_time": 151216.0,
      "text": "it is insecurity and violence"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 151240.0,
      "end_time": 155656.0,
      "text": "that stops them from achieving their full freedom and development."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 155680.0,
      "end_time": 159696.0,
      "text": "Now, they need basic security just as much as we do"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 159720.0,
      "end_time": 163560.0,
      "text": "and they need it so they can live a normal life"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 163800.0,
      "end_time": 165936.0,
      "text": "and so that they can enjoy their human rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 165960.0,
      "end_time": 168136.0,
      "text": "This is why we need to shift."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 168160.0,
      "end_time": 171160.0,
      "text": "We need to acknowledge that sustainable security"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 171400.0,
      "end_time": 173856.0,
      "text": "builds on a foundation of human rights,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 173880.0,
      "end_time": 177240.0,
      "text": "builds on promoting and respecting human rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 178320.0,
      "end_time": 180936.0,
      "text": "Also, over the past two decades,"
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 180960.0,
      "end_time": 185176.0,
      "text": "we have accepted that the best way to guarantee our own security"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 185200.0,
      "end_time": 187550.0,
      "text": "is by defeating our enemies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 187800.0,
      "end_time": 191800.0,
      "text": "and to do that, we need to rely almost exclusively on the military."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 192600.0,
      "end_time": 195696.0,
      "text": "Again, this clashes with my work, with my research,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 195720.0,
      "end_time": 197101.0,
      "text": "with what I see in the field."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 197125.0,
      "end_time": 200736.0,
      "text": "What I see is that building sustainable security"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 200760.0,
      "end_time": 203296.0,
      "text": "has a lot less to do with crushing enemies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 203320.0,
      "end_time": 205936.0,
      "text": "has a lot less to do with winning on the battlefield,"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 205960.0,
      "end_time": 208536.0,
      "text": "and has a lot more to do with protecting victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 208560.0,
      "end_time": 209960.0,
      "text": "and building stability."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 210760.0,
      "end_time": 213256.0,
      "text": "And to do that, well, the military alone"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 213280.0,
      "end_time": 214920.0,
      "text": "is simply insufficient."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 216280.0,
      "end_time": 221560.0,
      "text": "This is why I believe we need to shelve the never-ending War on Terror,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 221800.0,
      "end_time": 223656.0,
      "text": "and we need to replace it with a security agenda"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 223680.0,
      "end_time": 227616.0,
      "text": "that is driven by the principle of protecting civilians,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 227640.0,
      "end_time": 231550.0,
      "text": "no matter where they are from, what passport they hold,"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 231800.0,
      "end_time": 232696.0,
      "text": "or where they live:"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 232720.0,
      "end_time": 235960.0,
      "text": "Vancouver, New York,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 235120.0,
      "end_time": 238720.0,
      "text": "Kabul, Mosul, Aleppo or Douma."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 239600.0,
      "end_time": 242936.0,
      "text": "Sustainable security tells us that we&#39;re more likely"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 242960.0,
      "end_time": 246776.0,
      "text": "to have long-term security at home for ourselves"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 246800.0,
      "end_time": 250936.0,
      "text": "if we focus our engagements abroad on protecting civilians"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 250960.0,
      "end_time": 256696.0,
      "text": "and on ensuring their lives are lived in dignity and free from violence."
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 256720.00000000003,
      "end_time": 259976.00000000003,
      "text": "For example, we all know that defeating ISIS"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 260000.0,
      "end_time": 261776.0,
      "text": "is a security achievement."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 261800.0,
      "end_time": 263960.0,
      "text": "Absolutely."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 263120.0,
      "end_time": 266496.0,
      "text": "But rebuilding destroyed homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 266520.0,
      "end_time": 268455.0,
      "text": "restoring order,"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 268480.0,
      "end_time": 271656.0,
      "text": "ensuring a representative political system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 271680.0,
      "end_time": 274656.0,
      "text": "these are just as, if not more important,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 274680.0,
      "end_time": 278216.0,
      "text": "and not just for the security of civilians in Iraq and in Syria,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 278240.0,
      "end_time": 281600.0,
      "text": "but for our own security and for global stability."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 283200.0,
      "end_time": 284520.0,
      "text": "More fundamentally,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 285760.0,
      "end_time": 291176.0,
      "text": "ISIS&#39;s danger should not just be counted in the number of weapons it holds"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 291200.0,
      "end_time": 294656.0,
      "text": "but also in the number of children it has kept out of school"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 294680.0,
      "end_time": 296120.0,
      "text": "or indoctrinated."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 297400.0,
      "end_time": 299336.0,
      "text": "This is from a security perspective."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 299360.0,
      "end_time": 300976.0,
      "text": "From a security perspective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 301000.0,
      "end_time": 307160.0,
      "text": "the long-term generational impact of having millions of children in Syria"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 307400.0,
      "end_time": 311496.0,
      "text": "growing up knowing only war and out of school,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 311520.0,
      "end_time": 314816.0,
      "text": "this is a far more dangerous threat to stability"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 314840.0,
      "end_time": 317655.0,
      "text": "than all of ISIS&#39;s weapons combined,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 317680.0,
      "end_time": 323816.0,
      "text": "and we should spend just as much time and just as much energy to counter this"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 323840.0,
      "end_time": 328800.0,
      "text": "as what we spend when countering ISIS militarily."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 329480.0,
      "end_time": 333336.0,
      "text": "Over the past two decades, our security policy has been short-term."
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 333360.0,
      "end_time": 335936.0,
      "text": "It has focused on the here and now."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 335960.0,
      "end_time": 340296.0,
      "text": "It has systematically downplayed the link between what we do today"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 340320.0,
      "end_time": 341816.0,
      "text": "in the name of security"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 341840.0,
      "end_time": 344736.0,
      "text": "and the long-term impact of those choices."
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 344760.0,
      "end_time": 346936.0,
      "text": "In the years after 9/11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 346960.0,
      "end_time": 349150.0,
      "text": "some of the choices,"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 349400.0,
      "end_time": 351456.0,
      "text": "some of the policies we&#39;ve implemented"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 351480.0,
      "end_time": 356400.0,
      "text": "have probably made us less, not more secure in the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 356840.0,
      "end_time": 360560.0,
      "text": "Sustainable, civilian-centered security"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 360800.0,
      "end_time": 363376.0,
      "text": "needs to look at what happens in the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 363400.0,
      "end_time": 364679.0,
      "text": "Again, for example,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 365600.0,
      "end_time": 370536.0,
      "text": "relying on drones to target enemies in faraway countries may be a tool."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 370560.0,
      "end_time": 373776.0,
      "text": "It may be a tool to make sure or to lessen the threat"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 373800.0,
      "end_time": 376816.0,
      "text": "of an imminent attack on the United States."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 376840.0,
      "end_time": 380215.0,
      "text": "But what about the long-term impact?"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 380240.0,
      "end_time": 382496.0,
      "text": "If civilians are killed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 382520.0,
      "end_time": 385296.0,
      "text": "if communities are targeted,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 385320.0,
      "end_time": 388416.0,
      "text": "this will feed a vicious circle"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 388440.0,
      "end_time": 392496.0,
      "text": "of war, conflict, trauma and radicalization,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 392520.0,
      "end_time": 396216.0,
      "text": "and that vicious circle is at the center of so many of the security challenges"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 396240.0,
      "end_time": 397440.0,
      "text": "we face today."
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 398120.0,
      "end_time": 400520.0,
      "text": "This will not make us safer in the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 401960.0,
      "end_time": 405215.0,
      "text": "We need civilian security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 405240.0,
      "end_time": 408896.0,
      "text": "we need sustainable civilian-centered security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 408920.0,
      "end_time": 410456.0,
      "text": "and we need it now."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 410480.0,
      "end_time": 414136.0,
      "text": "We need to encourage thinking and research around this concept,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 414160.0,
      "end_time": 415640.0,
      "text": "and to implement it."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 416840.0,
      "end_time": 419296.0,
      "text": "We live in a dangerous world."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 419320.0,
      "end_time": 422159.0,
      "text": "We have many threats to peace and conflict."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 423720.0,
      "end_time": 425896.0,
      "text": "Much like in the days after 9/11,"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 425920.0,
      "end_time": 429760.0,
      "text": "we simply cannot afford not to think about international security."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 430840.0,
      "end_time": 434455.0,
      "text": "But we have to learn the lessons of the past 20 years."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 434480.0,
      "end_time": 437296.0,
      "text": "To get it right, to get security right,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 437320.0,
      "end_time": 439536.0,
      "text": "we need to focus on the long term."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 439560.0,
      "end_time": 441976.0,
      "text": "We need to focus on protecting civilians."
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 442000.0,
      "end_time": 444656.0,
      "text": "And we need to respect and acknowledge the fact"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 444680.0,
      "end_time": 449400.0,
      "text": "that sustainable security builds on a foundation of human rights."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 450200.0,
      "end_time": 453416.0,
      "text": "Otherwise, in the name of security,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 453440.0,
      "end_time": 455176.0,
      "text": "we risk leaving the world"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 455200.0,
      "end_time": 458656.0,
